{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"97920-comment-la-fourmi-sauva-la-colombe","title":"Comment La Fourmi Sauva La Colombe","description":"The land is dry and Little Ant is very thirsty. He goes to the river for a drink and is swept away.","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Isabelle  Duston","Veronique Biddau"],"illustrators":["Wiehan de Jager"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/97920-comment-la-fourmi-sauva-la-colombe"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141891/size3/134ad8caa3025116bcdc29245beb43da.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141891/size6/134ad8caa3025116bcdc29245beb43da.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141758/size6/80a5eaa41e8282b279289216a0be8874.jpg","text":"C'était une chaude\njournée d'été dans\nla forêt sèche.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141759/size6/b42bde69c9438b987b1802b046f43e7c.jpg","text":"La petite fourmi n'avait pas eu d'eau depuis plusieurs jours.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141760/size6/059c59be641f654ca3207a35a6a35bdf.jpg","text":"“J'ai besoin d'une goutte d'eau, même si elle tombe d'une feuille.”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141761/size6/85595a093c866e71d0019b2f8c9be7f6.jpg","text":"Mais même la rosée avait séché.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141762/size6/7814a77f591787ae4b967754eea2786f.jpg","text":"“Si je ne bois pas, je vais mourirv”, s'écria la petite fourmi. “Je dois aller à la rivière, dont j'ai entendu parler.”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141763/size6/cb5ff30542cdf30c74c9bd60ac835ef8.jpg","text":"“La rivière va t'emporter,” l'avertit un sage écureuil.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141764/size6/25f1761e78950f3d243b1a68c252324d.jpg","text":"Mais la petite fourmi avait trop soif. “Je vais mourir si je ne bois pas l'eau.”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141765/size6/9d4836efe3c5230feffa7f48975fd724.jpg","text":"9/29","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141766/size6/1ecdebe7df69064955a205aafc2046e8.jpg","text":"La petite fourmi partit chercher la rivière.\nDans l'herbe sèche et au dessus des branches sèches.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141768/size6/68fb9ad4a0f9be9de79aea7f49fc0813.jpg","text":"Jusqu'à ce qu'elle entende l'eau de la rivière.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141769/size6/f0c63907656b88559379e0632d82bf85.jpg","text":"La petite fourmi prit une grande gorgée d'eau fraîche.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141770/size6/68e1609389d2f358976071630b7391d1.jpg","text":"Elle était si heureuse qu'elle ne vit pas la vague montée.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141771/size6/4fafe0b010e3cff8e4108c3e94b69548.jpg","text":"La fourmi tenta de saisir l'herbe sèche flottant devant elle. Mais elle fut emportée par l'eau.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141772/size6/93e3c4a1b7728fdfb4fd29096d4a8e44.jpg","text":"“A l'aide. Aidez-moi s'il vous plaît.”","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141773/size6/b2bc5552befce42e3d837b501a9c2df8.jpg","text":"“Vite, montez”, déclara la colombe, en tenant une branche dans son bec.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141774/size6/651ca5247192faeb05e56e97a322e033.jpg","text":"17/29","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141775/size6/c429467dbcea394992b1e681692f168c.jpg","text":"“Je ne peux pas partir avant de dire merci à la colombe. Je vais attendre jusqu'à ce qu'elle revienne boire.”","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141776/size6/445a53607c9b52c1da005b403aedbfc0.jpg","text":"Un jour, alors qu'elle attendait, deux garçons arrivèrent à la rivière avec leurs lance-pierres.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141777/size6/53c1ec26a6621da8f3703d67554e8622.jpg","text":"“Il y a une grande colombe qui vient ici pour boire”, dit un garçon. “Nous l'aurons pour le dîner ce soir.”","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141778/size6/f14639abcaf79e0e28952c41be795589.jpg","text":"21/29","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141779/size6/c5ed43fc171accdddc37ff0865224e19.jpg","text":"“Je ne peux pas laisser ces garçons tuer la colombe. Mais je suis si petite, que puis-je faire?”","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141780/size6/ab970c114f6781d0c9040bdd3e4e26b0.jpg","text":"A ce moment là, la colombe descendit de l'arbre pour boire.","words":null},{"n":23,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141781/size6/c7921a901dd9692db02f6363696aca42.jpg","text":"24/29","words":null},{"n":24,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141782/size6/933bf05690c9ab563fda05a6e07d6fcc.jpg","text":"La petite fourmi eu une idée.","words":null},{"n":25,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141783/size6/6f6404332890b77e7418f2d60d6e17c5.jpg","text":"Elle sauta sur le pied d'un garçon, et le mordit aussi fort qu'elle put.","words":null},{"n":26,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141784/size6/5f416817e5bbb88cc4e7da3ab37db435.jpg","text":"Le garçon sauta. “Aïe!” S'écria-t-il.","words":null},{"n":27,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141785/size6/d92b41dd4d2a64977b767ab8be802d29.jpg","text":"La colombe fut surprise et s'envola dans un lieu sûr.","words":null},{"n":28,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141787/size6/6ceb24adf3188200acc101b6f25e2f39.jpg","text":"C'est ainsi que la petite fourmi remercia la colombe de lui avoir sauvé la vie.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":28,"words":298}}